column5: 10 minutes ago & mornings don't get much nicer than this
Looks great Lew, a morning rainbow.  Hopefully that is the end of the rain for awhile
~~~Yes another great day in down town Tarona,(TO to you out siders) Police chopper hovering over head, protesters camping out in the park a block away, Union Station jammed with Police waiting
I guess my mornings going better than yours...

hey oldphart,  were they drumming late into the night ? heard the noise was a major issue for those living in close vicinity. got ear plugs if ya need them  I think it'll peter out as it doesn't seem like the occupy community in toronto is cohesive (can't decide on what they wanna do and in fact splinter off into separate protests)  and lew, that is a killer rainbow to wake up to !
Nice Scene  Now where are the slime pictures. This is your rutting time Lew  Peter
Yeah ...  we better enjoy them while we have them.   Ain't gonna be too long until that white stuff starts flying around.
I am a lil ant in the concrete jungle too today.  But Mcdonalds had free coffee, now we are hyper ants.  Nice shot Lew, you've put in your time in the big smoke, you deserve the view.
Figures the pot of gold sets on your man cave
Can't think of a better place for all that gold Phil
Yeah Lew,those pictures of your garage are sweet.  Hey wow.There's a rainbow in the back ground.
Great picture for sure, love the colors!

awesome shot lew....i think i saw the same rainbow  my morning was awesome...up all night with a crying almost 2 year old....get 3 hrs sleep, wake up, timmies screws up my coffee, driver to work....highlight of the day was the 6 hour walk in the bush for my search and rescue requalification, hit timmies and they mess up my order again this time large with milk means large double double (cream and sugar) yuck...then drive home to find that I had forgotten to take the garbage out now my house smells funky... i blame the government lol
I recognize that spot.........   Doesn't get much better than that Lew!
